on march 15, 2021, after a-year of the-declaration of the-community-quarantine in metro-manila, #dutertepalpak went trending on social-media.
netizens blamed the-government for the-resurgence of cases and netizens lack of proper-response to the-pandemic but presidential-spokesperson-harry-roque said that the-new-variants of the-virus caused the-resurgence.
