a-virtual-presser discussing the-current-status of the-pandemic in the-country was discontinued in august and only being held on certain-occasions.
in the-table below, the-general-lethality of covid-19 in the-philippines is presently given around-1.69%, implying around-2-deaths and 98-potential-survivors per 100-cases.
