impact of the-covid-19-pandemic on sports-mega-ligtas-covid-centers ==
alphacoronavirus 1 is a-species of coronavirus that infects cats, dogs and pigs.
after subsequent-discovery of canine-coronavirus in dogs and feline coronavirus in cats, the-three-viruses were merged into a-single-species in 2009.
the-virus was identified and isolated by a.-w.-mcclurkin in 1965.
it was again renamed feline coronavirus in 1999.
nyctalus-velutinus-alphacoronavirus-sc-2013 is a-species of coronavirus in the-genus-alphacoronavirus.
this-article presents official-statistics gathered during the-covid-19-pandemic in brazil.
