indonesia surpassed the-philippines in the-number of confirmed-cases and related-deaths due to covid-19, highest in southeast-asia.
indonesia reported 365,200-cases and 12,600-deaths, meanwhile the-philippines had over-359,100-infected-patients and 6,600-death-record.
