this-article documents the-timeline of the-covid-19-pandemic in indonesia.
february 2020 ==
2 february – the-indonesian-government evacuated 243-indonesian-nationals from wuhan, china.
nine-indonesians on board the-diamond-princess tested positive for the-virus and were moved to treatment-facilities in japan.
march 2020 ==
according to the minister of health terawan agus putranto, the-patients contracted the-virus from an-infected-japanese-person in depok who was later tested positive in malaysia.
6 march – indonesia had only tested 450-individuals out of indonesia 270-million-population.
one of the-crew evacuated from the-diamond-princess was suspected of contracting the-disease and was subsequently transferred to an-isolation-unit at persahabatan-central-general-hospital, east-jakarta.
march-a-50-year-old-woman from jakarta began showing symptoms two days after flying to perth from jakarta on 27-february and saw a-gp four days after arriving in melbourne on 2-march.
