symptoms include diarrhea, vomiting, and anorexia.
the-virus is destroyed by most-available-disinfectants.
a-serological-study in 2006 has also shown antibodies to crcov to be present in dogs in canada and the-united-states.
this-article presents statistics covering the-covid-19-pandemic in thailand.
(sars-cov-2), the-virus which causes coronavirus-disease 2019 (covid-19)
the-first-human-cases of covid-19 were identified in wuhan, the-capital of the-province of hubei in china in december 2019.
