montreal was called "the epicentre of the-pandemic in canada.
companies that use "a-bridge-financing-facility for large-employers that need help to get through the-economic-downturn caused by the-coronavirus will have to commit to respect collective-bargaining-agreements, protecting workers’-pensions, and support national-climate-goals.
rules on access to the-money will place limits on dividends, share buy-backs and executive-pay.
the-government has selected diasorin to manufacture the-tests.
