a-drug for lung-inflammation (acute-respiratory-distress-syndrome) to treat the-worst-symptoms of coronavirus and prevent the-need for ventilation.
the-inflammatory-response to coronavirus causes lung-damage that can lead to respiratory-failure and death in severe-cases.
it is hoped the-treatment will also lead to patients spending fewer days dependent on oxygen and shorter-periods of time in hospital, reducing the-burden on healthcare-systems.
