the-first-three-coronavirus-cases included two-men that recently returned from italy and a-female-relative.
on the-same-day, the-government decided to scale down the-grand-ceremony planned for sheikh-mujibur-rahman's-birth-centenary on 17-march.
after they complained about the-unsanitary-conditions there, many of they were allowed to go home with advice to self-isolate.
